K01D0006-2_H0006-2:193a-19: de khyo dang bu las bral bas yi chad par gyur nas /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:193a-20: gcig pu gos gcig gis smad g-yogs te /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:193a-23: chu bo rnams kyi sgra dang /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:193a-24: bya'i sgra du ma rnams mnyan cing thos nas /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:193a-27: kyi hud bu chung ngu ma zhes zer zhing snying rje zhing brtse bas /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:193a-28: mchi mas brnangs bzhin du ngu ste /

K01D0006-2_H0006-2:193a-31: de ma thag tu 'di'i pha dang ma dang khyim
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:193b-0: gyi skye @193b bo mang po dag gnam lcags kyis
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:193b-1: phog ste shi'o // de'i nang nas skyes pa gcig cig thar te /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:193b-2: snying rje zhing brtse bas mchi mas brnangs bzhin du
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:193b-3: myur bar 'gro zhing de'i mdun logs su 'ongs pa
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:193b-4: dang / mos de skrag pa lta bur mthong nas /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:193b-5: kye skyes bu ci'i phyir rings par rgyug /

K01D0006-2_H0006-2:193b-15: khyo dang gnyen bshes dang yang ba dag bral ba //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:193b-16: bdag 'gro khyim na gnas par mi rigs te //

K01D0006-2_H0006-2:193b-18: khyim stong de dag tu ni gnas pa bla; ;khyim na gnas pa sdig ste cir mi rung //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:193b-19: mya ngan sdug bsngal rnam par 'phel bar 'gyur //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:193b-20: der phyogs gcig tu zhugs te song nas /

K01D0006-2_H0006-2:194a-0: des de la ngal bsos nas de dang lhan cig tu ras 'khal ba @194a *//
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:194a-2: de na thag pa khye'u gzhon nu gzhan zhig rang gi bzos 'tsho ba la zhugs te /

K01D0006-2_H0006-2:194a-28: dri dang me tog gis brgyan pa 'ba' zhig ma yin gyi /

K01D0006-2_H0006-2:194b-27: khyim de yang khyod nyid dbang byed kyi mi dga' bar ma byed cig /

K01D0006-2_H0006-2:196a-1: med pas gar dga' bar 'gro ste /

K01D0006-2_H0006-2:252a-11: gang ngan song la rab tu bab /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:252a-12: gang ngan song las byung ste /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:252a-13: mtho ris dang thar pa la rab tu gzhag par bya /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:252a-14: dge ba'i rtsa ba ma bskyed pa rnams la dge ba'i rtsa ba bskyed par bya /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:252a-15: gang bskyed pa rnams yongs su smin par bya /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:252a-16: gang yongs su smin pa rnams ni grol bar bya'o //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:252a-19: rgya mtsho chu srin gnas de ni //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:252a-20: dus las gal te yol yang srid //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:252a-21: gdul bar bya ba'i bu rnams la //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:252a-22: sangs rgyas dus las 'da' mi mdzad //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:252a-23: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis 'dzum pa mdzad pa dang /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:252a-24: chos nyid kyis nam gyi tshe sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das der 'dzum pa mdzad pa de'i tshe /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:252a-25: zhal nas 'od zer sngon po dang /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:252a-30: kha cig ni steng du dong ngo //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:252a-31: gang 'og tu dong ba de dag gis ni /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:252a-41: shin tu chu bur can dang /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:252b-3: padmo chen po lta bu dag gi sems can dmyal bar song nas /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:252b-4: gang tsha ba'i sems can dmyal ba der bab na ni bsil bar gyur /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:252b-5: gang grang ba'i sems can dmyal ba der bab na ni dro bar gyur te /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:252b-6: des sems can de dag gi sdug bsngal gyi khyad par slar bde bar gyur pa /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:252b-7: de dag 'di snyam du sems so //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:252b-10: 'on te gzhan zhig tu skyes snyam mo //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:252b-11: de dag dang ba bskyed pa'i phyir /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:252b-12: bcom ldan 'das kyis sprul pa der btang ngo //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:252b-13: de dag sprul pa de mthong nas /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:252b-14: de dag 'di snyam du sems so //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:252b-15: kye bdag cag ni tshe 'di nas shi 'phos pa'am /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:252b-16: gzhan du skyes pa ni ma yin mod kyi /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:252b-17: sngon chad ma mthong ba'i sems can 'di'i mthus na /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:252b-18: bdag cag gi sdug bsngal gyi khyad par bde bar gyur to //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:252b-20: de dag sprul pa la mngon par sems dad pa
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:252b-21: las de dag sems can dmyal ba'i sdug bsngal gyi
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:252b-22: las zad nas / gang du bden pa rnams kyi snod 'gyur ba der lha dang /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:252b-23: mi'i phyir nyid mtshams len to //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:252b-24: gang steng gi phyogs su dong pa des ni /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:253a-9: 'og min gnas kyi lha dag gi drung du song nas /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:253a-15: tshigs su bcad pa gnyis kyang brjod do //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:253a-16: 'byung ba la ni brtsam par byos //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:253a-17: sangs rgyas bstan la nan tan gyis //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:253a-18: 'chi bdag sde rnams gzhom pa ni //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:253a-19: ba glang gis ni rtsva khyim bzhin //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:253a-21: bag yod pa ru su spyod pa //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:253a-22: skye ba'i 'khor ba spong ba ste //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:253a-23: sdug bsngal ba yi mthar byed 'gyur //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:253a-24: de nas 'od zer de dag stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i 'jig rten kyi khams bskor nas /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:253a-25: bcom ldan 'das kyi snam gyi phyi bzhin 'brang zhing 'ong ngo //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:253a-26: de ste bcom ldan 'das kyis 'das pa lung bstan par bzhed na ni /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:253a-27: bcom ldan 'das kyi snam logs su mi snang bar 'gyur ro //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:253a-28: ma 'ongs pa lung bstan par bzhed na ni /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:253a-29: mdun du mi snang bar 'gyur ro //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:253a-30: sems can dmyal bar lung bstan par bzhed na ni /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:253a-31: zhabs kyi mthil du mi snang bar 'gyur ro //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:253a-32: byol song du skye bar lung bstan par bzhed na ni /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:253a-33: zhabs kyi rting par mi snang bar 'gyur ro //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:253a-34: yi dvags su skye bar lung bstan par bzhed na ni /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:253b-0: zhabs kyi mthe bor @253b mi snang bar 'gyur ro //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:253b-1: mir skye bar lung bstan par bzhed na ni /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:253b-2: pus mo gnyis su mi snang bar 'gyur ro //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:253b-3: stobs kyi 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal por lung bstan par bzhed na ni /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:253b-4: phyag g-yon pa'i mthil du mi snang bar 'gyur ro //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:253b-5: 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal por lung ston par bzhed na ni /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:253b-6: phyag g-yas pa'i mthil du mi snang bar 'gyur ro //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:253b-7: lhar skye bar lung ston par bzhed na ni /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:253b-8: lte bar mi snang bar 'gyur ro //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:253b-9: nyan thos kyi byang chub tu lung ston par bzhed na ni /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:253b-10: zhal gyi nang du mi snang bar 'gyur ro //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:253b-11: rang sangs rgyas kyi byang chub tu lung ston par bzhed na ni /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:253b-12: mdzod spur mi snang par 'gyur ro //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:253b-13: bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu lung ston par bzhed na ni /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:253b-14: gtsug tor gyi nang du mi snang bar 'gyur ro //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:253b-15: de nas 'od zer de dag bcom ldan 'das la lan gsum du bskor ba byas te /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:253b-16: bcom ldan 'das kyi zhal du mi snang bar gyur to //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:253b-17: de nas tshe dang ldan pa kun dga' bos thal mo sbyar te /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:253b-19: rnam pa sna tshogs kha dog stong gis brgyan //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:253b-20: zhal gyi nang nas mang po 'byung ba dag /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:253b-21: thams cad phyogs su gang gis snang mdzad pa //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:253b-22: snang byed shar bas ji ltar de bzhin no //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:253b-23: yang tshigs su bcad de smras pa /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:253b-24: 'phyar ba med cing mi dga' dregs spangs pa /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:253b-25: sangs rgyas skye bo mchog gi rgyur gyur te //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:253b-26: rgyu ma mchis par dung dkar padmo'i rtsa //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:253b-27: 'dzum pa mi ston rgyal ba dgra pham mdzad //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:254a-1: kyi rtogs pa bstan pa'i blo //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:254a-2: nyan pa rgyal dbang la ni thos par 'tshal //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:254a-3: thub pa khyu mchog gtan tshigs dam pas ni //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:254a-4: the tshom skyes pa mchog gis bsal bar mdzod //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:254a-5: mgon po brtan pa rgya mtsho'i ri bo bzhin //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:254a-6: rgyu med par ni sangs rgyas bzhad mi mdzad //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:254a-7: brtan pas gang gi phyir ni 'dzum bstan pa //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:254a-8: skye bo mang po 'di dag thos par 'tshal //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:254a-9: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:254a-14: rgyu med rkyen med par de bzhin gshegs pa dgra
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:254a-15: bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas dag
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:254a-17: kun dga' bo khyod kyis bu mo chos sbyin ma la dge slong ma'i dge 'dun dang /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:254a-18: nga'i bkas dge slong ma autpa la'i kha dog ma phrin par btang ste /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:254a-19: skyabs su 'gro ba gsum nas rim bzhin du rab
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:254a-20: tu phyung ba la lo gnyis kyi bar du chos
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:254a-21: drug dang / rjes su 'brang ba'i chos drug gi bslab pa'i sdom pa yang byin no //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:254a-22: de ni sang bag mar gtong ste /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:254a-23: de'i phyir skye bo mang po 'dus pa rnams mthong ngam /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:254a-27: bu mo de slar khyim du mi mor gnas pa'i skabs ma yin /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:254a-29: dga' bar bya ba'i phyir 'dod pa'i longs spyod la longs spyad pa'i gnas su 'di mi 'gyur gyi /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:254a-30: 'di ni da phyir mi ldog pa'i 'bras bu thob ste /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:254b-0: @254b dgra bcom pa mngon du byed par 'gyur ro //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:254b-2: dge slong ma rnams la 'di ltar chos sbyin mas ni /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:254b-3: lo gnyis kyi bar du chos drug dang /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:254b-4: rjes su 'brang ba'i chos drug gi bslab pa la bslabs zin gyi /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:254b-5: de la autpa la'i kha dog ma phrin par thong la /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:254b-6: de tshangs par spyad pa bskyed pa'i sdom pa byin par bsgo zhig /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:254b-9: tshe dang ldan pa kun dga' bos bcom ldan 'das kyi ltar mnyan te /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:254b-10: dge slong ma la bsgo ba dang /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:254b-11: dge slong ma'i dge 'dun gyis kyang autpa la'i kha dog ma phrin par bsgos te btang ngo //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:254b-12: de song nas bu mo khyod ni dge slong ma'i
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:254b-13: dge 'dun gyis tshangs pa spyad pa bskyed pa'i sdom
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:254b-14: pa gnang gi / da ni khyod bsnyen par rdzogs par bya'o //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:254b-15: ci nas 'di lta bu'i chos bshad de /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:254b-16: des thos ma thag tu slar phyir mi ldog pa'i 'bras bu mngon du byas nas /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:254b-18: autpa la'i kha dog ma song nas /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:254b-20: bcom ldan 'das kyis tshe dang ldan pa kun dga' bo la bka' stsal pa /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:254b-25: autpa la'i kha dog ma phrin par thong ste /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:254b-26: bu mo chos sbyin ma bsnyen par rdzogs par gyis shig /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:254b-30: tshe dang ldan pa kun dga' bos /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:255a-2: dge slong ma'i dge 'dun gyis kyang dge 'dun sde gnyis ka bsdus te /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:255a-3: chos sbyin ma khyim de na 'dug bzhin du /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:255a-4: autpa la'i kha dog ma las phrin gyis bsnyen par rdzogs par byas te /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:255a-5: autpa la'i kha dog ma song ste /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:255a-8: dge 'dun sde gnyis kyis bsnyen par rdzogs par byas so; ;zhes bsgo'o //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:255a-9: 'di lta bu'i chos kyang bshad de /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:255a-11: dge slong ma chos sbyin mas 'khor ba'i 'khor lo dum bu lnga po 'di g-yo pa dang /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:255a-13: 'dus byas kyi dngos po thams cad 'jig pa /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:255a-16: rnam par zhig pa'i chos nyid kyis rab tu bcom ste /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:255a-17: nyon mongs pa thams cad spangs te /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:255a-18: dgra bcom pa mngon du byas nas; dgra bcom par gyur te /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:255a-19: khams gsum gyi 'dod chags dang bral ba /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:255a-21: nam mkha' dang lag mthil ltar chags pa med pa
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:255a-22: bzhin du mnyam pa'i sems ste'u dang tsan dan du
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:255a-23: 'dra ba / ma rig pa'i sgo nga'i sbubs bcom pa /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:255a-26: so sor rig pa rnams thob pa /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:255a-27: srid pa'i 'dod chags la chags pa dang /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:255a-28: bkur sti la rgyab kyis phyogs pa /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:255a-31: lhar bcas pa rnams kyis mchod pa dang /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:255b-0: tshig gis snyan par @255b brjod par 'gyur ro //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:255b-1: dgra bcom pa'i dge slong ma /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:255b-3: khyim pa khyim na gnas pa'i skabs ma yin /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:255b-5: dga' ba bya ba'i phyir 'dod pa'i longs spyod la yongs su spyod pa'i gnas ma yin no //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:255b-6: nam chos sbyin ma dgra bcom pa mngon du byas pa dang /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:255b-9: yum bdag gis ni dgra bcom pa mngon du bgyis kyi /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:255b-10: rgyal po'i kun dga' ra bar dge slong ma'i dbyar mo khang du mchi na gnang bar mdzod cig /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:255b-13: chung ma dang gnyis gros byas nas bu mo de
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:255b-14: ltar na bdag cag la rgyal pos gyod rmas par
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:255b-15: mi 'gyur ram / de la rim bzhin du byas te /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:255b-16: bcom ldan 'das dang lhan cig tu song zhig /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:255b-21: de nas khyim bdag byin pas sangs rgyas bcom ldan
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:255b-22: 'das la sogs pa dge slong gi dge 'dun dag
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:255b-24: khyim bdag ri dvags sgra la /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:255b-26: bu mo chos sbyin ni khyim du gnas su mi btub ste /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:255b-27: rab tu 'byung bar gdon mi zas /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:255b-29: de nan gyis blang bar gyis shig /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:255b-31: khyim bdag ri dvags sgras yul ko sa la'i rgyal po gsal rgyal la gsol nas /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:255b-35: skye bo mang po dag sdud pa la zhugs so //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:255b-36: khyim bdag byin pas de'i nub mo gtsang zhing bsod pa'i bza' ba dang /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:256a-3: chu bum pa bkang ste bzhag /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:256a-4: bcom ldan 'das la spyan 'dren pas btsun pa bshos kyang lags /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:256a-5: gdugs tshod la yang bab na /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:256a-6: bcom ldan 'das dus la bab par dgongs shig /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:256a-8: de nas bcom ldan 'das snga dro'i dus na sham thabs gsol /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:256a-11: dge slong mang po dag gis bskor /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:256a-12: dge slong gi dge 'dun gyi mdun du byas te /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:256a-13: khyim bdag byin pa'i khyim gang na ba der gshegs so //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:256a-15: dge slong gi dge 'dun gyi mdun du stan bting ba la bzhugs so //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:256a-16: de nas khyim bdag byin pas mdza' bo dang /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:256a-20: dge slong gi dge 'dun dag bde bar bzhugs par shes nas /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:256a-21: gtsang zhing bsod pa'i bza' ba dang /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:256a-22: bca' ba dag nyid kyis lag dar te tshim pa dang /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:256a-24: de'i skabs su khyim bdag ri dvags sgras mdza' bo dang /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:256a-30: ljongs kyi skye bo mang po dang lhan cig tu sa ga srung ba dang /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:256a-31: bkra shis dang; zhi ba dag byas te /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:256a-32: bag ma len par chas te /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:256a-33: khyim bdag byin pa'i sgo drung na gnas shing 'khod do //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:256a-34: khyim bdag byin pas sangs rgyas dang /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:256b-0: dge slong gi dge 'dun la @256b bdag nyid kyis lag dar te /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:256b-3: bcom ldan 'das bshos gsol zin nas /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:256b-5: lhung bzed blangs par shes nas /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:256b-6: stan dma' ba zhig bting nas /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:256b-7: bcom ldan 'das kyi spyan sngar chos mnyan pa'i phyir mdza' bo dang /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:256b-10: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis khyim bdag byin pa /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:256b-13: gnyen dag la chos kyi gtam gyis yang dag par bstan /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:256b-16: yang dag par mgu bar byas so //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:256b-17: chos kyi gtam gyis rnam grangs du mar yang dag par bstan /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:256b-21: gdan las bzhengs nas bzhud do //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:256b-22: dge slong ma chos sbyin ma yis khams gsum gyi ni gnyen po thob /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:256b-24: de bag mar blangs pa'i dus la bab nas /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:256b-25: khyim bdag ri dvags sgra'i bu sa gas kyang mdza' bo dang /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:256b-31: ljongs kyi skye bo mang po dang lhan cig tu der sil snyan rnam pa sna tshogs 'byin te /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:256b-33: bcom ldan 'das kyi phyi bzhin phyir 'byung bar 'dod pa dang /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:256b-34: de nas khyim bdag ri dvags sgra'i bu sa gas 'phral la dpung pa brkyang nas /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:256b-35: chos sbyin gyi lag pa nas bzung bar brtsam pa dang /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:257a-2: sems can grangs med pa brgya stong gis mthong bzhin
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:257a-3: du ngang pa'i rgyal po 'dab ma brkyang pa bzhin
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:257a-5: rnam pa sna tshogs kyi cho 'phrul bstan pa dang /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:257a-6: de na khyim bdag ri dvags sgra'i mdza' bo dang /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:257a-12: ljongs kyi skye bo mang po dang; khyim bdag ri dvags sgra'i bu sa ga dang /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:257a-13: gzhan yang ltad mo la lhags pa'i sems can dag ngo mtshar cher gyur nas /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:257a-14: shing rtsa ba nas bcad pa bzhin du rkang pa la phyag 'tshal nas; sring mo /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:257a-15: 'di 'dra ba'i yon tan mang po thob na /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:257a-16: khyod 'dod chags la spyod pa'i skabs ma yin te /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:257a-19: de nas chos sbyin ma nam mkha' las babs te /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:257a-20: skye bo mang po dag gi mdun du 'dug nas 'di lta bu'i chos bshad de /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:257a-21: sems can mang po brgya stong gis thos nas /

K01D0006-2_H0006-2:423a-13: grong khyer rtsva can du gshegs nas tha ma'i gzims mal du zhugs kyi /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:423a-14: de la chos mnyan pa'i phyir der 'dong bar bya'o //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:423a-16: kho bo ni re zhig glu dbyangs len gyi /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:423a-18: de nas yang lha'i dbang po brgya byin gyis /

K01D0006-2_H0006-2:423a-22: bcom ldan 'das tha ma'i gzims mal du zhugs te /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:423a-23: yongs su mya ngan las 'da' bar 'gyur gyi //

K01D0006-2_H0006-2:423a-31: nyan thos kyis gdul bya la ni /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:423b-0: de bzhin gshegs pas @423b 'dul bar spyad kyi /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:423b-1: sangs rgyas kyis gdul ba ni nyan thos kyis 'dul mi nus pas /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:423b-2: de lta bas na de bzhin gshegs pas gdul bar bya bar mkhyen pa ni /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:423b-4: ma la 'di bdag gis gdul bar bya gor ma chag snyam du dgongs nas /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:423b-5: ji ltar thugs mnyam par snyoms par zhugs na /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:423b-6: tha ma'i gzims mal du sprul pa bzhag nas /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:423b-8: khog pa bee d'ur++ya las byas pa bsnams te /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:423b-9: tha ma'i gzims mal nas byung nas /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:423b-10: sum cu rtsa gsum pa'i lha rnams kyi nang /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:423b-11: dri za'i rgyal po rab dga'i sgo na bzhugs par
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:423b-12: 'gyur ba de lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:423b-13: par zhugs so // dri za'i rgyal po rab dga' yang gang nga lta bu ni med do //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:423b-14: zhes dri za'i rgyal po rab dga' dregs par gyur te /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:423b-15: des pi wang snyan pa snyan pa blangs nas yid rab tu dga' bar gyur cing 'dug go /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:423b-16: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis sgo srung gi skyes bu la 'di skad ces bka' stsal to //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:423b-18: dri za'i rgyal po rab dga' la sgo khar dri za zhig shes ldan blta ba'i phyir 'ongs so //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:423b-20: de song nas smras pa dang /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:423b-21: de dregs pas myos nas smras pa /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:423b-23: ci nga las gzhan pa'i dri za yang yod dam /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:423b-25: gzhan dag lta re zhig smos kyang ci 'tshal gyi /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:423b-26: sgo drung 'di kho na na mchis lags so //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:423b-27: dri za de dregs pas myos pa'i shugs kyis mod la sgor byung ste /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:424a-1: pa; kva'e skyes bu khyod dri za yin nam /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:424a-2: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:424a-3: kva'e nga dri za te por yin no //

K01D0006-2_H0006-2:424a-6: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:424a-7: kva'e legs kyi de bzhin bya'o //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:424a-8: zhes ji tsam bcom ldan 'das dang /

K01D0006-2_H0006-2:424a-11: des kyang rgyud gcig bcad de /

K01D0006-2_H0006-2:424a-14: bcom ldan 'das kyis rgyud gnyis bcad pa dang /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:424a-15: de bzhin du sgra dang gdangs khyad par med do //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:424a-16: de bzhin du gsum pa dang /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:424a-17: bzhi pa nas rgyud gcig pa'i bar du bzhag pa dang /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:424a-18: rab dgas kyang gnyis pa dang /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:424a-20: bzhi pa nas rgyud gcig pa'i bar du gzhag ste /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:424a-21: de bzhin du pi wang gnyis ka skad dang /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:424a-23: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis rgyud gcig pa yang bcad de /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:424a-24: nam mkha' kho na la yang sgra dang gdangs de bzhin du gyur pa dang /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:424a-25: dri za'i rgyal po rab dga' ngo mtshar skyes nas nga rgyal gyis dregs pa med par gyur nas /

K01D0006-2_H0006-2:424b-29: rus pa'i ri bo las ni bsgral /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:424b-30: ngan song gi sgo dag ni bkum /

K01D0006-2_H0006-2:425a-6: ji srid 'tsho'i bar du srog gcod pa las log
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:425a-7: ste / mngon par dad nas skyabs su mchi lags so //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:425a-8: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis dri za'i rgyal po
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:425a-9: rab dga' la chos dang ldan pa'i gtam gyis yang
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:425a-10: dag par bstan / yang dag par 'dzin du bcug /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:425a-12: yang dag par rab tu dga' bar mdzad do //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:425a-13: ji ltar thugs mnyam par bzhag na sum cu rtsa
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:425a-14: gsum pa'i lha rnams kyi nang nas mi snang bar
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:425a-15: gyur cing / tha ma'i gzims mal du bzhugs pa
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:425a-16: de lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:425a-17: gyur cing / so // de'i tshe grong khyer rtsva can na /

K01D0006-2_H0006-2:425a-28: 'gram au du ma w'a ra'i tshal gyi drung na
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:425a-29: / nyin par gyi spyod pas gnas pa dang /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:425a-30: gang gi tshe bcom ldan 'das byang chub sems dpa'
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:425a-31: dga' ldan gyi gnas na bzhugs pa gzigs pa lngas
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:425b-0: gzigs te / 'dod pa na spyod pa'i lha drug la @425b lan gsum du sbyang ba mdzad nas /

K01D0006-2_H0006-2:426a-4: au dum w'a ra'i tshal rnyings par 'gyur ba de

K01D0006-2_H0006-2:426a-7: grong khyer rtsva can pa la de bzhin gshegs pa

K01D0006-2_H0006-2:427a-5: 'di ltar me tog au dum w'a ra bzhin no //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:427a-7: bcom ldan 'das go'u ta ma de /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:427a-8: deng gi mtshan mo'i gung thun la phung po lhag

K01D0006-2_H0006-2:427a-11: bdag ni chos rnams la the tshom yod par gyur te /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:427a-12: bdag gi the tshom yod pa de 'di ltar bcom ldan 'das go'u ta mas /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:427a-13: bdag gi the tshom sel spyod par 'gyur ro //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:427a-14: snyam du bdag sems shing mchis te /

K01D0006-2_H0006-2:427b-0: / gsan nas @427b kyang tshe dang ldan pa kun dga' bo la 'di skad ces bka' stsal to //

K01D0006-2_H0006-2:432b-12: de nas thams cad kyis rgal nas /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:432b-13: gang kha cig slar rgal bar ma gyur tam /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:432b-14: zhes de dag la snying rje bskyed de /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:432b-15: slar rgyab tu bltas pa dang /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:432b-16: ri dvags kyi phru gu gcig ma rgal bar des mthong nas /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:432b-17: de nas khyu dpon gnad rnams ni chad /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:432b-18: tshigs rnams ni 'bye ba'i tshor ba gnad du bab pa byung zhing /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:432b-19: chu 'gram 'dir tshogs rnams la srog sdug pa'i skyabs byas shing /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:432b-20: ri dvags kyi phru gu de rgyab tu bkal nas /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:432b-21: chu bo las bsgral te 'gram du bzhag go /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:432b-22: des ri dvags kyi tshogs mang po rgal bar rig nas /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:432b-23: 'chi ba'i dus su smon lam gdab par brtsams pa /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:432b-24: ji ltar bdag gis ri dvags 'di dag dang /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:432b-25: ri dags kyi phru gu 'di la srog sdug pa'i skyabs byas shing /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:432b-26: nyon mongs pa las kyang kun tu bskyabs pa 'dis /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:433a-0: bdag bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub mngon @433a *//
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:433a-1: par rdzogs par sangs rgyas pa na yang /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:433a-4: bde ba mthar phyin par byed cing /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:433a-5: mya ngan las 'das pa la 'god par shog cig /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:433a-7: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:433a-8: dge slong dag ji snyam du sems /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:433a-9: de'i tshe de'i dus na ri dvags kyi khyu dpon gang yin pa de ni nga yin no //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:433a-10: ri dvags de dag ni grong khyer rtsva can gyi gyad 'di rnams yin no //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:433a-11: ri dvags kyi phru gu gang yin pa de ni rab bzang 'di nyid yin no //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:433a-12: dge slong dag gzhan yang gang gi tshe /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:433a-13: nga brtag cing 'jig mi nus pa dang /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:433a-14: dud 'gro'i skye gnas su skyes pa dang /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:433a-16: tshigs rnams ni 'byed pa'i tshor ba gnad du bab par byung zhing bzhugs bzhin du /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:433a-17: kun tu rgyu rab bzang gi skyabs byas pa de nyon cig /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:433a-18: dge slong dag sngon byung ba 'das pa'i dus na /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:433a-19: yul w'a ra n'a sir rgyal po tshangs sbyin zhes bya ba zhig /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:433a-20: rgyal po byed pa 'byor pa dang /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:433a-24: skye bo dang mi mang pos gang ba /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:433a-28: 'khrug pa rnams rab tu zhi ba /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:433a-34: ma he phun sum tshogs pa /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:433a-35: chos kyi rgyal po chos dang ldan pa /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:433b-0: chos bzhin @433b du rgyal po byed pa de'i rta cang shes shi ba dang /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:433b-1: khams kyi rgyal phran dag gis 'di ltar /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:433b-2: rgyal po tshangs sbyin gyi rta cang shes shi'o //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:433b-4: de dag gis der pho nya btang nas /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:433b-5: yang na ni dpya gcol cig /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:433b-6: yang na ni grong khyer gyi sgor ma 'byung zhig /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:433b-7: gzhan du na nges par ske nas btags la 'dir 'gug go /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:433b-10: grong khyer gyi sgor yang ma byung mod kyi /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:433b-11: 'on kyang grong khyer nyid na gnas shing rta cang shes tshol lo //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:433b-12: de dus gzhan zhig na rta cang shes rnyed nas de de la zhon te /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:433b-13: dpyid kyi dus la bab pa dang /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:433b-14: shing rnams me tog gis rgyas shing /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:433b-21: shang shang te'u yi sgra 'byin pa'i nags tshal skyed
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:433b-22: mos tshal gyi gnas su btsun mo'i 'khor gyis yongs
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:433b-24: de; de na rtse zhing dga' la /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:433b-25: dga' mgur cha ba'i sbyor bas bag med par gnas te /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:433b-26: grong khyer du yang ma zhugs pa na /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:433b-27: ji ltar rgyal po tshangs sbyin skyed mos tshal na bag med par gnas shing /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:433b-28: grong khyer du yang ma bzhugs so //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:433b-29: zhes khams kyi rgyal phran dag gis thos te /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:433b-30: de dag gis gros byas nas /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:433b-31: dpung gi tshogs yan lag bzhi dang chas te /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:433b-32: yul w'a ra n'a si'i sgo bskor ba dang /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:433b-33: blon pos rgyal po tshangs sbyin la smras pa /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:434a-0: lha khams kyi rgyal phran rnams kyis grong khyer @434a *//
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:434a-2: bde bar bgyi ba dgongs su gsol /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:434a-4: shes ldan rta cang shes gang na 'dug pa yang long zhig /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:434a-5: dpung gi tshogs yan lag bzhi yang go skon cig /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:434a-6: de dag dang lhan cig g-yul 'gyed par bya'o //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:434a-8: des rta cang shes kyang bsnyen /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:434a-9: dpung gi tshogs yan lag bzhi pa yang go bskon te /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:434a-10: de de dag dang lhan cig g-yul bshams te /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:434a-12: khams kyi rgyal phran gzhan zhig gis rgyal po tshangs
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:434a-13: sbyin gyi rta cang shes kyi glor mdung gcig bsnun
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:434a-14: nas / de'i rgyu ma dag byung ste sdug bsngal gyi tshor bas gzir nas /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:434a-16: tshigs rnams kyang 'bye ba'i tshor ba gnad du bab pa byung bzhin du /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:434a-18: ma la 'di ltar rgyal po ni /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:434a-19: sdug bsngal dog pa nyam nga bar phyin la /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:434a-20: bdag gis dor bar bya ba ni bdag gi tshul ma yin pas /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:434a-21: brtson 'grus kyis sdug bsngal bzlog la /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:434a-22: thabs ci dang cis sge'u chung nas grong khyer du phyin par bya'o //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:434a-24: phan tshun du grong khyer du 'gro ba'i glags bltas na /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:434a-25: w'a ra n'a si'i skyed mos tshal gyi bar na /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:434a-26: rgyal po tshangs sbyin gyi rdzing bu tshangs ldan zhes bya ba /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:434b-0: padma dkar po dag gis brgyan @434b pa; ngang pa dang /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:434b-1: bya ka ran da ba dang /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:434b-2: dur pa dag gis mtsho gling brgyan pa dang /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:434b-3: kho ra khor yug tu me tog dang /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:434b-5: nags tshang tshing gis brgyan pa /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:434b-6: bya rnam pa sna tshogs kyi sgra 'byin pa zhig yod de /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:434b-7: de shugs drag pos nags tshal stug po de'i nang du song ste /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:434b-8: rdzing bu tshangs ldan gyi padma'i 'dab ma nas padma'i
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:434b-9: 'dab ma'i steng du rkang pa bzhag nas rgal te
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:434b-11: de nas rgyal po babs pa dang /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:434b-15: blon po de rnams kyis phan tshun kun du btsal bar brtsams nas /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:434b-16: kha cig ni skyed mos tshal du song /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:434b-17: gzhan dag gis ni phyogs bzhir brgyugs nas /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:434b-18: gang gis kyang de ma rnyed nas rang rang gi rta dang /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:434b-19: glang po che dag bzung nas slar song ngo //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:434b-20: rgyal po tshangs sbyin gyis srog 'byin pa'i phyir /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:434b-21: de yul w'a ra n'a si na gnas pa'i grong mi dang /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:434b-23: blon po lhag ma dag bsdus nas /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:434b-25: gang rgyal rigs spyi bo nas dbang bskur ba'i srog byin na /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:434b-26: de la ji ltar bsgrub par bya /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:434b-28: lha rgyal srid kyi phyed stsal bar bgyi'o //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:434b-30: nga'i srog 'byin pa ni rta cang shes yin na /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:434b-32: de la byin yang des ci zhig byar yod /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:434b-34: lha de'i slad du grong khyer gyi sgo bzhir sbyin pa dag gtang bar bgyi zhing /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:435a-1: ma yin pa'i mchod ston dag bgyis la bsod nams dag bgyi'o //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:435a-4: legs kyi de bzhin du bya'o //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:435a-5: de nas rgyal po'i btsun mo dang /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:435a-8: yul mi dag gis shing dri zhim po thams cad spungs nas /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:435a-10: gzhan yang grong khyer gyi sgo bzhir sbyin gtong gi khang pa brtsigs nas /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:435a-11: grong khyer de na rdo dang /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:435a-13: gyo mo dag sel du bcug ste /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:435a-14: tsandan gyi chus ni chag chag btab /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:435a-15: dri zhim po'i pog por dag ni bzhag /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:435a-18: dar gyi lda ldi mang po ni btags /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:435a-19: lha rnams kyi dga' tshal gyi skyed mos tshal bzhin
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:435a-20: du me tog rnam pa sna tshogs kyi sil ma
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:435a-21: nyams dga' ba ni bkram ste; dus ston ma yin
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:435a-23: grong khyer du 'di skad dril bsgrags pa /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:435a-25: yul w'a ra n'a si na gnas pa'i grong mi rnams dang /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:435a-26: yul sna tshogs nas 'ongs pa'i skye bo'i tshogs dag nyon cig /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:435a-27: 'dir lha'i rta cang shes kyi phyir grong khyer gyi sgo bzhir sbyin pa gtong zhing /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:435a-28: dus ston ma yin pa'i mchod ston dang bsod nams byed kyi /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:435a-29: de'i phyir khyed cag rnams kyis gos sna tshogs dang /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:435a-32: 'byor pa mchog gis chos la byung zhig /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:435a-34: de nas grong mi dag dang /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:435b-0: @435b dus ston ma yin pa'i mchod ston chen po byas te /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:435b-1: grong khyer gyi sgo bzhir yang 'dod pa sna tshogs kyi sbyin pa dag sbyin no //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:435b-4: rta cang shes gang yin pa de ni nga nyid yin te /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:435b-5: de'i tshe de'i dus na yang na gnad rnams ni chad /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:435b-6: tshigs rnams ni 'bye ba'i tshor ba gnad du bab
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:435b-7: pa byung bzhin du de'i srog gi skyabs byas so
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:435b-10: de nas yang dge slong rnams the tshom skyes te /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:435b-11: the tshom thams cad gcod pa sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das la zhus pa /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:435b-13: tshe dang ldan pa rab bzang gis las ci zhig bgyis na /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:435b-14: de nas nyan thos rnams kyi tha mar mngon sum du bgyis lags /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:435b-15: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:435b-17: dge slong rab bzang nyid kyis las byas shing bsags pa dang /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:435b-20: 'od pa bzhin du nye bar gnas pa /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:435b-21: myong bar nges par rab bzang gis las byas shing bsags pa dag ni /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:435b-22: gzhan su zhig gis nyams su myong bar 'gyur /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:435b-23: dge slong dag las byas shing bsags pa dag ni
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:435b-24: phyi rol gyi sa'i khams la smin par mi 'gyur
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:435b-25: te / chu'i khams la ma yin /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:435b-27: rlung gi khams la ma yin mod kyi /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:435b-30: skye mched rnams la las byas pa'i dge ba dang /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:436a-0: mi dge ba dag rnam par smin par @436a *//
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:436a-2: las rnams bskal pa brgyar yar ni //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:436a-3: chud mi za ba'ang tshogs dang dus //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:436a-4: rnyed na lus can rnams la ni //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:436a-7: sngon byung ba 'das pa'i dus bskal pa bzang po
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:436a-8: 'di nyid la skye dgu rnams kyi tshe lo nyi
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:436a-10: ston pa 'od srung zhes bya ba 'jig rten du byung ste /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:436a-11: rig pa dang zhabs su ldan pa /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:436a-15: skyes bu 'dul ba'i kha lo sgyur ba /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:436a-16: lha dang mi rnams kyi ston pa sangs rgyas bcom
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:436a-17: ldan 'das de yul w'a ra n'a si'i grong khyer
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:436a-18: ri dvags 'dzin gyi tshal na nye bar rten cing
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:436a-19: bzhugs so // de nas bcom ldan 'das 'od srung
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:436a-20: gi dbon po mya ngan med ces bya ba de
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:436a-21: thar par bya ba'i don du /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:436a-22: bcom ldan 'das 'od srung las rab tu byung ste /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:436a-23: de thar cing rang dbang thob bo //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:436a-24: snyam nas 'bad pa ma bskyed do //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:436a-25: ji tsam na dus shin tu ring ba zhig na /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:436a-26: mya ngan med ces bya ba ljongs rgyu zhing 'dug par gyur to //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:436a-27: bcom ldan 'das yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas 'od srung gis /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:436a-28: sangs rgyas kyi mdzad pa ma lus par mdzad nas
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:436a-29: bud shing zad pa'i me bzhin du tha ma'i gzims
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:436a-31: dge slong mya ngan med shing aa sho ka'i drung na nang du yang dag 'jog la gnas te /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:436b-0: ji tsam shing aa sho ka de la lha zhig @436b gnas pa des /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:436b-1: bcom ldan 'das 'od srung mya ngan las 'da' bar thos nas ngus te /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:436b-2: de ngus pa'i mchi ma thig pa gcig mya ngan med kyis lus la lhung bar gyur pa dang /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:436b-3: de nas mya ngan med kyis gyen du bltas na /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:436b-5: lha ci'i phyir ngu zhes smras pa dang /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:436b-6: lhas deng gi mtshan mo'i gung thun la bcom ldan 'das 'od srung mya ngan las 'da'o //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:436b-7: zhes smras so; ;de nas mya ngan med lha'i tshig thos nas /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:436b-8: gnad du phog pa bzhin 'gyel te /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:436b-9: de snying rje rje skad du ngu zhing 'dug par gyur to //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:436b-10: de nas lhas ci'i phyir du //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:436b-12: mya ngan med kyis smras pa /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:436b-14: bla ma dang bral ba'i phyir te /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:436b-15: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas 'od srung ni bdag gi zhang po yin no //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:436b-16: bdag gis shin tu sbyangs shing gnas pa la ma
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:436b-17: 'bad pas bdag ni so so'i skye bor gyur la
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:436b-18: / lam shin tu ring bas blta ma nus so //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:436b-21: gal te de lta na bdag gis bcom ldan 'das kyi spyan sngar bkri na /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:436b-22: ci khyad par rtogs par nus sam /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:436b-23: mya ngan med kyis smras pa /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:436b-24: ci ltar lhas bcom ldan 'das kyi zhal mthong bar bgyis na /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:436b-25: bdag gi blo ni kun tu smin te /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:436b-26: de bzhin du khyad par rtogs par bgyi'o //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:436b-27: de nas lhas bcom ldan 'das kyi spyan sngar mya ngan med rdzu 'phrul gyis khrid de /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:436b-28: des bcom ldan 'das mthong nas dad pa skyes so //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:437a-1: ldan 'das 'od srung gis chos rnam pa 'di lta bu dag bshad de /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:437a-2: de thos ma thag tu dgra bcom pa mngon sum du byas te /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:437a-3: dang por tshe dang ldan pa mya ngan med mya ngan las 'das so //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:437a-4: de nas bcom ldan 'das yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas 'od srung ngo //
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:437a-5: de nas lha des tshe dang ldan pa mya ngan med mya ngan las 'das par mthong ste /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:437a-8: tshe dang ldan pas gang cung zad khyad par rtogs pa de thams cad ni /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:437a-9: bdag las brten pa yin gyi /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:437a-10: bdag ma 'ongs pa'i dus na gang bram ze'i khye'u
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:437a-11: bla ma la bcom ldan 'das 'od srung gis bram
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:437a-12: ze'i khye'u khyod skye dgu rnams kyi tshe lo brgya
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:437a-13: thub pa na / ston pa sh'akya thub pa zhes
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:437a-14: bya ba de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:437a-15: dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas su 'gyur ro zhes
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:437a-17: tha ma'i gzims mal du gshegs pa na /
K01D0006-2_H0006-2:437a-18: bdag de'i nyan thos rnams kyi tha mar mngon sum du byas nas /
